            <div type="translation" source="bib:GopinathaRao1988_01">
                <p>The king Aḻakaṉ Kulaśekhara, the ruler of the earth, deciding that the work done by his elder brother on the beautiful <foreign>gopura</foreign>, which is praised even by the celestials, should not remain thus incomplete, finished it fully with brick.</p>
            </div>      
            
            
            
